description: Gets metadata information about the test set.

parameters.name: testSetId
parameters.description: The test set Id for the test set request.

nested_items.name: testSetId
nested_items.description: The test set Id for the test set response.

nested_items.name: testSetName
nested_items.description: The test set name of the test set.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the test set.

nested_items.name: modality
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the test set is audio or text data.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the test set.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The roleARN used for any operation in the test set to access resources in the Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: numTurns
nested_items.description: The total number of agent and user turn in the test set.

nested_items.name: storageLocation
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 storage location for the test set data.

nested_items.name: s3BucketName
nested_items.description: The name of the Amazon S3 bucket in which the test set is stored.

nested_items.name: s3Path
nested_items.description: The path inside the Amazon S3 bucket where the test set is stored.

nested_items.name: kmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of an Amazon Web Services Key Management Service (KMS) key for encrypting the test set.

nested_items.name: creationDateTime
nested_items.description: The creation date and time for the test set data.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time for the last update of the test set data.
